Ön Genius kedvezményre jogosult Duplex na orla da praia do forte com hidro e Wi-Fi szálláshelyén! Hogy spórolhasson ezen a szálláson, csupán be kell lépnie.

Boasting air-conditioned accommodation with a balcony, Duplex na orla da praia do forte com hidro e Wi-Fi is situated in Cabo Frio. This beachfront property offers access to a terrace, free private parking and free WiFi. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk and a lift for guests. The spacious apartment has 4 bedrooms, a flat-screen TV, a fully equipped kitchen with an oven and a microwave, a washing machine, and 3 bathrooms with a hot tub. The accommodation is non-smoking. For those times when you'd rather not dine out, you can choose to cook on the barbecue. Dining options are available close to the apartment. Guests at Duplex na orla da praia do forte com hidro e Wi-Fi will be able to enjoy activities in and around Cabo Frio, like fishing and hiking. Popular points of interest near the accommodation include Praia do Forte, Water Square and Surf Museum. The nearest airport is Cabo Frio International Airport, 7 km from Duplex na orla da praia do forte com hidro e Wi-Fi.
